&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to recruit an enthusiastic, dynamic, experienced Pre-operative assessment senior nurse to lead our established nursing team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will run our thriving Pre-operative assessment unit at Central Middlesex Hospital. They will need to be highly motivated, organised and be able to be work flexibly in a busy environment. Your role will also include clinical responsibilities and managerial responsibilities leading your own team of staff nurses and facilitating the future development of the unit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; You will act as a clinical expert and a visible role model and provide specialist knowledge, professional leadership and support to staff within the unit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are passionate about constantly improving our service and delivering high quality care to our patients. We are looking for committed individual with excellent organisational and interpersonal skills, who have a genuine interest in Pre operative assessment to join our team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
